INSERT INTO `locations` VALUES (1,'GoWork BSD Green Office Park','https://go-work.com','089656496064','BSD Green Office Park Jl. BSD Green Office Park, BSD City, Tangerang 15345','https://g.page/GoWorkBSD?share','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3965.722195748409!2d106.649723013841!3d-6.300187663411359!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2e69fb92e658abdd%3A0xcb99b05f3290fe54!2sGoWork%20BSD%20Green%20Office%20Park%20-%20Coworking%20and%20Office%20Space!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1578826395143!5m2!1sen!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','GoWork\nBSD GREEN OFFICE PARK\nWhen we think of BSD, we think of expansion. Our location in Green Park Office will provide you access to one of the liveliest business districts in the Greater Jakarta Metropolitan Area. We\'ve transformed the entire floor into a highly functional workspace, powered by technology and the pursuit of Collaboration. Located in the center of the BSD Business District, GoWork Green Park Office will have you in direct access of a growing hub of modern business, and only minutes away from AEON Mall and the Indonesia Convention Exhibition complex. If you\'re looking to have your business in the place to be, book your tour today!','2020-01-12 18:05:50','2020-01-12 18:05:50','gowork-bsd-green-office-park','Tangerang','sales@go-work.com'),(2,'Apiary','http://apiary.id/','0818165222','Menara Global 15th Floor Jl. Jend. Gatot Subroto Kav. 27. Kuningan, Jakarta Selatan 12950. Indonesia','https://goo.gl/maps/SKBc3FLWt4u5zn2m9','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15864.975806776843!2d106.8214536!3d-6.231537!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x275e5e1788209e5f!2sApiary%20Coworking%20Space%20(Kuningan)!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578827606718!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Designed with thriving startups, creative entrepreneurs, and independent professionals, Apiary aims to be a platform that fosters creative collaborations between community members by promoting entrepreneurship, diversity and productive work environment.\nWe are more than just a coworking space in Jakarta – we are a family that grows together.','2020-01-12 18:19:18','2020-01-12 18:19:18','apiary','Jakarta Selatan','https://www.facebook.com/apiary.coworking'),(3,'Arkamaya','https://www.arkamayaculinary.com/','08119233777','Jl. Jend Gatot Subroto Kav. 51-52, Ruko A9 Petamburan, Slipi Jakarta Pusat – 10260','https://goo.gl/maps/6CtiRrSBrqwRLPYs9','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15865.85364913405!2d106.8006901!3d-6.2024351!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xd99ba33e252e129c!2sArkamaya%20Indonesian%20CREATIVE%20Culinary%20Education!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578828372008!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','\nInspired by the food industry that keeps developing as fast as poaching an egg, Arkamaya offers a first-class culinary education of Indonesian cuisine in the heart of Jakarta.\n\nIt is our belief that everyone has that creative soul and hunger for greatness. Accordingly, we have built a diverse range of programs (academy and short courses) for every person fond of Indonesian food, either a professional or an everyday learner. Each lesson will simmer your creativity to take that familiar taste from your mother’s kitchen, mix it well, and turn it into something new.','2020-01-12 18:29:51','2020-01-12 18:29:51','arkamaya','Jakarta Pusat','info@arkamayaculinary.com'),(4,'Sweet Troops','https://sweettroops.com/','085945912722','Jl. Teuku Nyak Arief Blok G no: 16 RT/RW 007/003 Kel. Grogol Selatan Kec. Kebayoran Lama. Jakarta Selatan, DKI Jakarta 12220, Indonesia','https://goo.gl/maps/BU5y6cRmWGM4kkXb9','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15864.9693515461!2d106.7886037!3d-6.2317505!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x8364205b4079fa30!2sSweet%20Troops!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578828803541!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Welcome to Sweet Troops Artisan Baking Studio.  Established in 2016 by Livianca Venaessa.\n\nOur beautiful baking studio offers hands on pastry classes ranging from baking to decorating workshops specially crafted for all level of learners. Focusing on professional as well as enjoyable class atmosphere, conducted by local and international tutors will ensure the students to get qualified learning experiences.\n\nWe cannot wait to cake away with you soon!','2020-01-12 18:39:24','2020-01-12 18:39:24','sweet-troops','Jakarta Pusat','ask.sweettroops@gmail.com'),(5,'Union Space','https://unionspace.id/','081295784299','Lantai 16, Mega Kuningan, Jl. Prof. DR. Satrio C4, RT.7/RW.2, Jl. Kuningan Barat Raya, RT.7/RW.2, Kuningan, Kuningan Tim., Kecamatan Setiabudi, Jakarta, Daerah Khusus Ibukota Jakarta 12950','https://goo.gl/maps/KRXfte8PZUwoovNG8','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d7932.58159979432!2d106.828221!3d-6.225336!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xee3d85e6081430f7!2sUnionSPACE%20-%20Satrio%20Tower%20(Serviced%20Office%20%7C%20Event%20Space%20%7C%20Virtual%20Office%20%7C%20Meeting%20Room)!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sid!4v1578831045313!5m2!1sen!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','FintechSPACE powered by UnionSPACE is Indonesia\'s first specialized Fintech co-working space and in collaboration with Fintech Indonesia Association (AFTECH), with the aim of assisting the growth of business ecosystems in Indonesia especially in Fintech industry.\n\nStrategically located in Satrio Tower, Kuningan, FintechSPACE is targeted to officially commencing in June 2018. It is expected to be a platform for collaboration among stakeholders in the field of technology, including members of AFTECH, regulators, finance companies, venture capital firms, and startups.\n\nFintechSPACE will be the space for various activities, ranging in the form of seminars, workshop, and mentoring to support entrepreneurs and business owners. It can be a sphere for members to collaborate, exchange ideas and solutions, as a means to create new innovations, and become the center for network development to accelerate the growth of the Indonesian Fintech industry.','2020-01-12 19:16:59','2020-01-12 19:16:59','union-space','Jakarta Pusat','https://www.instagram.com/unionspace.id/'),(6,'Werkspace','https://www.werkspace.id/','02150515088','SOHO CAPITAL Podomoro City, 19th Floor, Jl. Letjen. S. Parman Kav. 28, Tanjung Duren Selatan, Grogol Petamburan, Jakarta Barat 11470','https://goo.gl/maps/jj96WgxVgFYm62sQ6','<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d15866.690084535552!2d106.7897985!3d-6.1745788!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xa2260e416b98e583!2sWerkspace%20Soho%20Capital!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1578831733949!5m2!1sid!2sid\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>','Soho Capital\nThis beautiful location occupies the entire 19th Floor of Soho Capital\'s Premium Grade-A Office Tower, spread across a floor space of 1,500 m2. With sweeping views of the city skyline and direct access to West Jakarta\'s busiest commercial, office, shopping and residential \"Central Park Superblock\". It offers excellent cost to benefit ratio combined with unsurpassed convenience, which makes this location highly desirable for both local and multinational companies. Available services from coworking space, serviced office, virtual office, meeting rooms, conference rooms and event space. Demand is consistently high so whatever your office requirements, contact us today to ensure availability for you and your team. ','2020-01-12 19:24:02','2020-01-12 19:24:02','werkspace','Jakarta Barat','https://www.instagram.com/werkspace.id/');
