INSERT INTO `rooms` VALUES (1,1,'Event Space',1,30,'EVENT SPACE\n30 pax classroom setup','2020-01-12 18:05:50','2020-01-12 18:05:50'),(2,1,'Event Space - Large',20,150,'EVENT SPACE\n20-150 pax talkshow setup','2020-01-12 18:05:50','2020-01-12 18:05:50'),(3,1,'MEETING ROOM',1,10,'Meeting Room 10 pax','2020-01-12 18:05:50','2020-01-12 18:05:50'),(4,2,'Event Space',1,80,'EVENT SPACE\nCapacity: 80 pax (classroom)','2020-01-12 18:19:18','2020-01-12 18:19:18'),(5,2,'Event Space',1,100,'EVENT SPACE\nCapacity: 100 pax (theater)','2020-01-12 18:19:18','2020-01-12 18:19:18'),(6,3,'Cooking Studio',36,40,'Kitchen rental Jakarta - With an area of 340sqm, our state-of-the-art kitchen space is a truly a chef’s dream. There are two studios available for your cooking and baking needs, both are fully equipped with commercial and domestic appliances.\n\nWhether it’s a pastry workshop or recipe-testing before opening a restaurant, our 7 fully self-contained work stations are perfect to expand your culinary business. Pastry course Jakarta.\n\nCooking Studio Facilities:\n\nFood processor, Salamander, Four-burner stove, Deck oven, Griller, Hand blenders, Mixers, Vacuum pack machine, Blast chiller, Manual pasta maker\n\nBaking Studio Facilities:\n\nHand blenders, Hand and standing mixers, Dough sheeter, Deck ovens, Traditional ovens, Convection ovens, Under-counter chiller and freezer, Blast chiller','2020-01-12 18:29:51','2020-01-12 18:29:51'),(7,3,'Pastry Studio',40,45,'Kitchen rental Jakarta - With an area of 340sqm, our state-of-the-art kitchen space is a truly a chef’s dream. There are two studios available for your cooking and baking needs, both are fully equipped with commercial and domestic appliances.\n\nWhether it’s a pastry workshop or recipe-testing before opening a restaurant, our 7 fully self-contained work stations are perfect to expand your culinary business. Pastry course Jakarta.\n\nCooking Studio Facilities:\n\nFood processor, Salamander, Four-burner stove, Deck oven, Griller, Hand blenders, Mixers, Vacuum pack machine, Blast chiller, Manual pasta maker\n\nBaking Studio Facilities:\n\nHand blenders, Hand and standing mixers, Dough sheeter, Deck ovens, Traditional ovens, Convection ovens, Under-counter chiller and freezer, Blast chiller','2020-01-12 18:29:51','2020-01-12 18:29:51'),(8,4,'Sweet Troops Room',1,13,'MAXIMUM SPACE CAPACITY\n13 Pax – Seating Class Arrangement\n\nTOOLS\nStandard baking tools such as metal bowls, rubber spatula, cake tins, digital scale, portable stove, trays, turn table, glass, tablespoon etc.\n\n*Kindly bring your own portable stove gas refill\n\nFREEZER & CHILLER\nUpright 640 x 800 x 1830 mm\n\n*Kindly inform us how much space you will need in advanced\n\nOVEN\nTwo decks gas & electric oven for four 60 x 40cm trays\n\nCLEANING SERVICE\nCleaning agents such as dish washing soap, hand soap etc\nCleaning assistant\n*Kindly bring your own kitchen towel','2020-01-12 18:39:24','2020-01-12 18:39:24'),(9,4,'Sweet Troops Room',38,40,'MAXIMUM SPACE CAPACITY\n38 – 40 – Full Sitting Arrangement\nTOOLS\nStandard baking tools such as metal bowls, rubber spatula, cake tins, digital scale, portable stove, trays, turn table, glass, tablespoon etc.\n\n*Kindly bring your own portable stove gas refill\n\nFREEZER & CHILLER\nUpright 640 x 800 x 1830 mm\n\n*Kindly inform us how much space you will need in advanced\n\nOVEN\nTwo decks gas & electric oven for four 60 x 40cm trays\n\nCLEANING SERVICE\nCleaning agents such as dish washing soap, hand soap etc\nCleaning assistant\n*Kindly bring your own kitchen towel','2020-01-12 18:39:24','2020-01-12 18:39:24'),(10,5,'Classroom',1,60,'FintechSPACE powered by UnionSPACE is Indonesia\'s first specialized Fintech co-working space and in collaboration with Fintech Indonesia Association (AFTECH), with the aim of assisting the growth of business ecosystems in Indonesia especially in Fintech industry.\n\nStrategically located in Satrio Tower, Kuningan, FintechSPACE is targeted to officially commencing in June 2018. It is expected to be a platform for collaboration among stakeholders in the field of technology, including members of AFTECH, regulators, finance companies, venture capital firms, and startups.\n\nFintechSPACE will be the space for various activities, ranging in the form of seminars, workshop, and mentoring to support entrepreneurs and business owners. It can be a sphere for members to collaborate, exchange ideas and solutions, as a means to create new innovations, and become the center for network development to accelerate the growth of the Indonesian Fintech industry.','2020-01-12 19:16:59','2020-01-12 19:16:59'),(11,5,'Talkshow',1,150,'FintechSPACE powered by UnionSPACE is Indonesia\'s first specialized Fintech co-working space and in collaboration with Fintech Indonesia Association (AFTECH), with the aim of assisting the growth of business ecosystems in Indonesia especially in Fintech industry.\n\nStrategically located in Satrio Tower, Kuningan, FintechSPACE is targeted to officially commencing in June 2018. It is expected to be a platform for collaboration among stakeholders in the field of technology, including members of AFTECH, regulators, finance companies, venture capital firms, and startups.\n\nFintechSPACE will be the space for various activities, ranging in the form of seminars, workshop, and mentoring to support entrepreneurs and business owners. It can be a sphere for members to collaborate, exchange ideas and solutions, as a means to create new innovations, and become the center for network development to accelerate the growth of the Indonesian Fintech industry.','2020-01-12 19:16:59','2020-01-12 19:16:59'),(12,5,'Meeting Room',1,10,'FintechSPACE powered by UnionSPACE is Indonesia\'s first specialized Fintech co-working space and in collaboration with Fintech Indonesia Association (AFTECH), with the aim of assisting the growth of business ecosystems in Indonesia especially in Fintech industry.\n\nStrategically located in Satrio Tower, Kuningan, FintechSPACE is targeted to officially commencing in June 2018. It is expected to be a platform for collaboration among stakeholders in the field of technology, including members of AFTECH, regulators, finance companies, venture capital firms, and startups.\n\nFintechSPACE will be the space for various activities, ranging in the form of seminars, workshop, and mentoring to support entrepreneurs and business owners. It can be a sphere for members to collaborate, exchange ideas and solutions, as a means to create new innovations, and become the center for network development to accelerate the growth of the Indonesian Fintech industry.','2020-01-12 19:16:59','2020-01-12 19:16:59'),(13,6,'Event Space',1,30,'Soho Capital\nThis beautiful location occupies the entire 19th Floor of Soho Capital\'s Premium Grade-A Office Tower, spread across a floor space of 1,500 m2. With sweeping views of the city skyline and direct access to West Jakarta\'s busiest commercial, office, shopping and residential \"Central Park Superblock\". It offers excellent cost to benefit ratio combined with unsurpassed convenience, which makes this location highly desirable for both local and multinational companies. Available services from coworking space, serviced office, virtual office, meeting rooms, conference rooms and event space. Demand is consistently high so whatever your office requirements, contact us today to ensure availability for you and your team. ','2020-01-12 19:24:02','2020-01-12 19:24:02');
